entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You delievered all the parts needed for the shuttle.
entries.journal_entry_description: Collect all the shuttle parts and deliver them to HX-138 so the mechanic can repair the Lambda Shuttle.
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Retrieve power converters from ship wreckage.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Find a complete replacement for the shuttle's spinal trunk.
entries.task05_task_display_string_2: You recovered a shuttle spinal trunk.
entries.task05_task_display_string_3: You recovered some shuttle computer core memory.
entries.task05_task_display_string_4: You recovered some shuttle power converters.
entries.task06_comm_message_text: [HX-138] Great work. Come back to my location and deliver the parts to the mechanic so he can resume repairs.
entries.task07_journal_entry_description: Speak to the Mechanic to deliver the parts.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: See if HX-138 has anything else for you.
